org.pikater.shared.database.jpa

Class JPABatch

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pikater.shared.database.jpa.JPAAbstractEntity
      • org.pikater.shared.database.jpa.JPABatch

  • @Entity
public class JPABatch
extends JPAAbstractEntity
    Class JPABatch represents record about a computation batch.

    Each of this class contains a list of experiments that form the actual batch.

      • setTotalPriority

        @Deprecated
public void setTotalPriority(int totalPriority)
        Deprecated. 
        Use this method with caution as it may break synchronization between user priority and user assigned priority.
        • To override priority by an administrator, use this method.
        • To initialize total priority of a new batch, use updateTotalPriority().

      • getTotalPriority
